Dialogue: 0,0:00:01.10,0:00:08.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Today we're going to be talking about what you are changes the world. So what
Dialogue: 0,0:00:08.78,0:00:14.87,Default,,0,0,0,,does that mean what you are changes the world? Because we all radiate a certain
Dialogue: 0,0:00:14.87,0:00:20.94,Default,,0,0,0,,energy from our own level of consciousness. So the higher your level of
Dialogue: 0,0:00:20.94,0:00:29.82,Default,,0,0,0,,consciousness the more profound effect you have on the world. So a town
Dialogue: 0,0:00:29.82,0:00:35.04,Default,,0,0,0,,goes along a certain way and one person enters this town who's never
