Dialogue: 0,0:00:59.52,0:01:01.72,Default,,0,0,0,,merely blessed by the fact that you you know
Dialogue: 0,0:01:01.72,0:01:12.32,Default,,0,0,0,,moved into the neighborhood. Of course the reverse is probably true. One bum does
Dialogue: 0,0:01:12.32,0:01:19.12,Default,,0,0,0,,not wreck a wreck a whole city you know but one that very advanced saintly saint
Dialogue: 0,0:01:19.12,0:01:29.42,Default,,0,0,0,,saintly person does reduce the crime rate and scientific research is
Dialogue: 0,0:01:29.42,0:01:31.70,Default,,0,0,0,,documented that that is actually a fact.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:32.64,0:01:41.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Well you talk about the broken window theory where you know that one building
Dialogue: 0,0:01:41.10,0:01:44.62,Default,,0,0,0,,in a town has a broken window and all of a sudden that whole neighborhood goes
Dialogue: 0,0:01:44.62,0:01:50.30,Default,,0,0,0,,down. Yes. Due to the fact that that broken window theory. It's called
Dialogue: 0,0:01:50.30,0:01:56.54,Default,,0,0,0,,detriment so the neighborhood goes down because of the one broken window. So it's
Dialogue: 0,0:01:56.54,0:02:02.72,Default,,0,0,0,,obvious that if we had one saintly person in the area that the whole
Dialogue: 0,0:02:02.72,0:02:05.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Area would go up for the same reasons
Dialogue: 0,0:02:06.02,0:02:11.80,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't know if that's been proven or not. I know the down downward has been proven
Dialogue: 0,0:02:12.50,0:02:16.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, let's ask the arm upward is equally
Dialogue: 0,0:02:17.42,0:02:19.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Demonstrable. Oh, okay
Dialogue: 0,0:02:20.00,0:02:25.87,Default,,0,0,0,,so the best thing that can happen to a community is that a person with a high level of consciousness moves into town and
Dialogue: 0,0:02:26.78,0:02:31.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Then the crime rate goes down. Actually the crime rate goes down. Wow. Okay
Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.84,0:02:38.02,Default,,0,0,0,,do you remember when you first came to town and you said that you were teaching the course of miracles when you first came to
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.02,0:02:40.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Sedona and that the course of miracles
Dialogue: 0,0:02:41.88,0:02:50.63,Default,,0,0,0,,almost a certain percentage of the population was doing the course of miracles because you had huge groups here when it first came to
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.63,0:02:52.63,Default,,0,0,0,,town and
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.63,0:02:58.83,Default,,0,0,0,,They had there was zero crime rate in Sedona at that time. Yes, Sedona had a zero crime rate. Yeah, and
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.69,0:03:02.49,Default,,0,0,0,,Just the
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.49,0:03:02.99,Default,,0,0,0,,course
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.99,0:03:03.07,Default,,0,0,0,,of
