Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.57,0:03:08.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Were sufficient to eliminate all crime
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.03,0:03:12.51,Default,,0,0,0,,There was no crime in Sedona at all zero
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.31,0:03:18.09,Default,,0,0,0,,So this goes back to what you are changes the world
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.67,0:03:25.25,Default,,0,0,0,,So that's true when you say it can one person have the effect on the entire world
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.88,0:03:31.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's say Jesus Christ did yeah, okay
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.30,0:03:33.80,Default,,0,0,0,,I mean
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.80,0:03:36.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Everybody wants to feel like they you know
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.82,0:03:44.00,Default,,0,0,0,,This is the old ego speaking. Everybody wants to feel like we because of me the world is changing. So what about that?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.00,0:03:44.68,Default,,0,0,0,,I mean
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.68,0:03:50.84,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't think people who change the world sedum self because to me the world is changing
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.26,0:03:53.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Well certain people I know would
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.30,0:04:00.08,Default,,0,0,0,,They have a very high ego. Yeah, but I mean I mean in reality who really are advanced
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.23,0:04:03.37,Default,,0,0,0,,Probably would never even think of the question
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.37,0:04:08.20,Default,,0,0,0,,it wouldn't come to their mind
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.20,0:04:12.70,Default,,0,0,0,,because it's just their normal way of life.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.50,0:04:15.68,Default,,0,0,0,,But that's correct.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.84,0:04:20.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Statistics show that the crime rate dropped to zero
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.44,0:04:25.15,Default,,0,0,0,,in Sedona when the Courts of Miracles people
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.15,0:04:26.33,Default,,0,0,0,,started to teach here.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.88,0:04:29.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Crime rate dropped to zero.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.11,0:04:32.53,Default,,0,0,0,,The crime rate is still zero.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.88,0:04:36.08,Default,,0,0,0,,The crime rate is still zero.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.08,0:04:40.63,Default,,0,0,0,,No, the crime rate has gone up since then?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.45,0:04:43.21,Default,,0,0,0,,The crime rate has gone up since then.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.43,0:04:45.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, because lots of people who don't calibrate high
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.77,0:04:46.79,Default,,0,0,0,,moved into town.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.91,0:04:48.39,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.53,0:04:48.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.85,0:04:52.09,Default,,0,0,0,,That makes sense.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.16,0:04:57.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay, you say that divinity is the essence.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.45,0:05:00.03,Default,,0,0,0,,All right, let me see what this is.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.48,0:05:07.93,Default,,0,0,0,,Divinity is the essence out of which my existence.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.51,0:05:09.71,Default,,0,0,0,,You told me that.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.79,0:05:10.13,Default,,0,0,0,,One time.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.53,0:05:13.27,Default,,0,0,0,,Divinity is the...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.27,0:05:14.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Source of my existence.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.91,0:05:16.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.37,0:05:16.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Right.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.57,0:05:19.21,Default,,0,0,0,,It is out of the Godhead that all arises.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.21,0:05:25.14,Default,,0,0,0,,It is out of the Godhead that all existence arises.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.86,0:05:28.22,Default,,0,0,0,,That is a fact.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.90,0:05:29.46,Default,,0,0,0,,There you go.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.10,0:05:30.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.74,0:05:37.94,Default,,0,0,0,,So if we held that phrase in mind in our daily lives,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.68,0:05:41.40,Default,,0,0,0,,would that help us to achieve
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.40,0:05:41.78,Default,,0,0,0,,what you want to achieve?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.78,0:05:46.92,Default,,0,0,0,,The fact that each and every one of us is valuable
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.92,0:05:50.33,Default,,0,0,0,,is important.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.56,0:05:55.78,Default,,0,0,0,,The realization that you are of value to the community
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.78,0:05:59.16,Default,,0,0,0,,automatically changes your behavior.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.27,0:06:06.22,Default,,0,0,0,,So just to have certain people move into town
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.22,0:06:09.89,Default,,0,0,0,,was the most beneficial thing that happened to that town.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.35,0:06:12.81,Default,,0,0,0,,It's that people of a high calibrated level
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.81,0:06:14.83,Default,,0,0,0,,have moved into town.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.83,0:06:16.44,Default,,0,0,0,,And when they did,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.46,0:06:18.34,Default,,0,0,0,,the crime rate dropped to practically zero.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.52,0:06:19.24,Default,,0,0,0,,It dropped to zero.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.65,0:06:25.23,Default,,0,0,0,,But if we were to make that statement,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.39,0:06:28.55,Default,,0,0,0,,divinity is the essence of my existence,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.53,0:06:32.09,Default,,0,0,0,,if we were to meditate on that,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.17,0:06:36.76,Default,,0,0,0,,would that eventually become who we were or who we are?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.20,0:06:38.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, it is who you are.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.58,0:06:39.94,Default,,0,0,0,,It's just that you don't realize it,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.04,0:06:42.52,Default,,0,0,0,,that divinity is the source of your existence.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.42,0:06:46.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Without God, none of us would be here.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.98,0:06:47.82,Default,,0,0,0,,I know.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.94,0:06:48.90,Default,,0,0,0,,There's no discussion today.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.10,0:06:52.66,Default,,0,0,0,,You know, it's very difficult for me to think that,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.57,0:06:55.93,Default,,0,0,0,,to, I mean, because you,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.89,0:07:01.41,Default,,0,0,0,,this would be a good phrase for me to hold in mind
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.41,0:07:05.13,Default,,0,0,0,,to live my life like that.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.21,0:07:09.86,Default,,0,0,0,,In other words, divinity is the existence,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.62,0:07:13.00,Default,,0,0,0,,I mean, divinity is the essence of my existence.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.62,0:07:16.92,Default,,0,0,0,,I mean, if we say that to ourselves like every morning,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.02,0:07:19.04,Default,,0,0,0,,don't you think that,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.04,0:07:22.38,Default,,0,0,0,,don't you think that would help us to live our life like?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.54,0:07:24.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Like a prayer, yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.52,0:07:24.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Like a prayer?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.94,0:07:25.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Mm-hmm.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.24,0:07:28.00,Default,,0,0,0,,And that we would change the world because of doing that?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.04,0:07:29.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, that would be a fact.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.66,0:07:29.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.34,0:07:30.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.04,0:07:32.94,Default,,0,0,0,,You could scientifically prove it.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.64,0:07:35.16,Default,,0,0,0,,That can be scientifically proven.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.58,0:07:36.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.40,0:07:38.08,Default,,0,0,0,,All right.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.48,0:07:40.66,Default,,0,0,0,,I just wanted to clarify that
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.66,0:07:43.00,Default,,0,0,0,,because I thought that was such a good phrase
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.00,0:07:47.66,Default,,0,0,0,,and I think that if you did kind of hold that in mind
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.66,0:07:49.50,Default,,0,0,0,,each morning before you got out of bed,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.58,0:07:54.80,Default,,0,0,0,,that it would help you to live your life like that
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.80,0:08:01.80,Default,,0,0,0,,as a person to where eventually it became a secondary.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.18,0:08:03.22,Default,,0,0,0,,It becomes a fact.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.24,0:08:04.62,Default,,0,0,0,,It becomes a fact, yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.18,0:08:07.52,Default,,0,0,0,,It just becomes a part of who you are.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.36,0:08:11.04,Default,,0,0,0,,In the beginning, it's a supposition based on faith
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.04,0:08:14.55,Default,,0,0,0,,and then it becomes progressively a reality
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.55,0:08:19.99,Default,,0,0,0,,and then one day you understand the reality behind it all.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.99,0:08:20.49,Default,,0,0,0,,Mm-hmm.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.51,0:08:22.29,Default,,0,0,0,,All right.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.61,0:08:31.86,Default,,0,0,0,,So who I am in spirit would be how we change the world?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.06,0:08:36.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Is that what you're saying when you say what you are changes the world?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.16,0:08:39.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Is that who you are in spirit, is that what changes the world?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.58,0:08:45.72,Default,,0,0,0,,It's the power of the energy that radiates from a divine being,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.84,0:08:47.24,Default,,0,0,0,,a more advanced being.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.24,0:08:52.69,Default,,0,0,0,,It goes up exponentially so that,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.13,0:08:58.60,Default,,0,0,0,,the more we purify ourself and try to be beneficial to the world,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.48,0:09:01.98,Default,,0,0,0,,the more we actually become so.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.38,0:09:02.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.70,0:09:05.62,Default,,0,0,0,,The more intention to be of service to the world
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.62,0:09:09.25,Default,,0,0,0,,and to reduce pain and suffering
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.25,0:09:15.85,Default,,0,0,0,,and in and of itself, that intention already changes the world.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.37,0:09:16.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Mm-hmm.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.08,0:09:19.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.70,0:09:23.50,Default,,0,0,0,,So when you talk about the ships floating on the sea
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.50,0:09:24.32,Default,,0,0,0,,and by...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.04,0:09:26.08,Default,,0,0,0,,You don't want to raise...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.08,0:09:27.90,Default,,0,0,0,,The ships, you've said that in other lectures.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.98,0:09:29.74,Default,,0,0,0,,You don't want to try and raise the ship
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.74,0:09:32.64,Default,,0,0,0,,because by ourself, if we try and raise the ship, it's impossible.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.88,0:09:33.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.10,0:09:37.72,Default,,0,0,0,,But if we raise the level of the water in which the ship is floating...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.72,0:09:38.20,Default,,0,0,0,,There you go.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.28,0:09:40.86,Default,,0,0,0,,...that that changes the whole concept.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.00,0:09:42.12,Default,,0,0,0,,That's very profound.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.70,0:09:42.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.98,0:09:48.74,Default,,0,0,0,,So that which we become begins to raise the level of the sea
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.74,0:09:51.32,Default,,0,0,0,,and the sea then lifts the ships
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.32,0:09:54.98,Default,,0,0,0,,so we all benefit by the saintly person.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.46,0:09:55.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Mm-hmm.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.76,0:09:56.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.18,0:09:58.40,Default,,0,0,0,,And the more saintly we can become,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.32,0:10:02.82,Default,,0,0,0,,the greater service we are to our fellow human being.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.14,0:10:03.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Mm-hmm.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.67,0:10:10.45,Default,,0,0,0,,So actually, we don't have to be out there in the forefront.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.53,0:10:14.35,Default,,0,0,0,,No, we don't have to be beating the drum, ringing the bell.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.52,0:10:20.27,Default,,0,0,0,,Just be the most perfect person you can become.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.48,0:10:22.88,Default,,0,0,0,,In the name of thee, O Lord,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.10,0:10:27.24,Default,,0,0,0,,I pray that my presence is of service to this world.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.56,0:10:27.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Amen.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.08,0:10:28.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Mm-hmm.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.00,0:10:36.51,Default,,0,0,0,,We serve God and our fellow man by becoming all that we can become.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.13,0:10:37.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Mm-hmm.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.30,0:10:50.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Sometimes, I mean, I've done this myself where I've gone in,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.30,0:10:54.96,Default,,0,0,0,,and like you always say, go into a store, smile at the clerk and say,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.06,0:10:56.56,Default,,0,0,0,,I want you to have a really good day.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.32,0:11:00.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Or, you know, boy, you look really happy today or whatever.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.50,0:11:03.84,Default,,0,0,0,,And it makes them just bright.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.20,0:11:06.56,Default,,0,0,0,,You know, you made their day by saying it.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.58,0:11:11.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, it's just one remark changes a person's whole day.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.98,0:11:15.70,Default,,0,0,0,,That's why I believe in being complimentary to acknowledge people's gift to the world.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.23,0:11:21.25,Default,,0,0,0,,You know, I mean, this carpet right here is vacuumed to perfection.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.23,0:11:23.69,Default,,0,0,0,,You know, there's no trash on the floor.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.87,0:11:26.35,Default,,0,0,0,,There's nothing, you know, I mean, everything is perfect.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.56,0:11:31.12,Default,,0,0,0,,So we acknowledge the gift that others have given us
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.12,0:11:36.48,Default,,0,0,0,,through their preparation for this interview right now.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.48,0:11:37.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Mm-hmm.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.44,0:11:37.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.66,0:11:39.40,Default,,0,0,0,,We have a nice couch for us to sit on.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.50,0:11:42.68,Default,,0,0,0,,The temperature in here is just fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.94,0:11:50.61,Default,,0,0,0,,And so I am grateful for the way it was set up for our interview, you know.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.75,0:12:02.04,Default,,0,0,0,,So if we were to, how, I want to ask you a question.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.12,0:12:07.38,Default,,0,0,0,,How do you, like, radiate love to someone who is not loving?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.28,0:12:11.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Who is not lovable or loving?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.32,0:12:12.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Who is not loving.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.26,0:12:15.12,Default,,0,0,0,,How do you radiate love?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.34,0:12:22.60,Default,,0,0,0,,And embrace that person when they're not always a loving person?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.48,0:12:26.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, well, they don't have to be loving all the time to be lovable.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.93,0:12:31.41,Default,,0,0,0,,Even the doggy piddles on the floor once in a while.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.61,0:12:35.63,Default,,0,0,0,,That's our fault because we don't let her out.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.95,0:12:36.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.83,0:12:38.37,Default,,0,0,0,,But we don't blame the dog.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.55,0:12:39.83,Default,,0,0,0,,We don't stop loving the dog.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.43,0:12:43.51,Default,,0,0,0,,We blame ourselves for our own shortcoming.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.51,0:12:47.16,Default,,0,0,0,,So if people are not polite,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.74,0:12:52.27,Default,,0,0,0,,appropriate in our, to us,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.97,0:12:56.19,Default,,0,0,0,,I always make the presumption that it's something in myself
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.19,0:12:58.53,Default,,0,0,0,,that they're perhaps reacting to,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.31,0:13:01.13,Default,,0,0,0,,of which I am unaware.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.91,0:13:05.17,Default,,0,0,0,,That I perhaps have an aversion to some aspect of their life
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.17,0:13:09.03,Default,,0,0,0,,or their lifestyle or their means of expression.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.46,0:13:12.80,Default,,0,0,0,,And so I say, well,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.80,0:13:17.68,Default,,0,0,0,,what am I contributing to this overall field of energy?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.48,0:13:21.56,Default,,0,0,0,,So whenever we come up against an obstacle,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.56,0:13:25.82,Default,,0,0,0,,we should also look within to see if we are creating that obstacle.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.82,0:13:27.98,Default,,0,0,0,,See what we could be contributing to it.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.98,0:13:28.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Right.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.48,0:13:28.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Mm-hmm.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.98,0:13:32.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Which, in other words, self-examination is the...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.30,0:13:35.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, it's the willingness to take responsibility for all that we can.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.46,0:13:35.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Right.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.96,0:13:38.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, people don't like to do that, you know.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.36,0:13:41.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, I didn't ask them if they liked it.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.26,0:13:44.94,Default,,0,0,0,,They don't like to pay taxes either.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.94,0:13:47.28,Default,,0,0,0,,But we ought to do it, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.28,0:13:48.64,Default,,0,0,0,,They'd put you in jail if you don't.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.64,0:13:54.18,Default,,0,0,0,,But it's true, you know.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.18,0:13:57.08,Default,,0,0,0,,There's so many people out there with negative attitudes and everything.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.08,0:13:58.10,Default,,0,0,0,,And I always want...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.10,0:14:02.78,Default,,0,0,0,,It's very difficult to be kind, loving, and gracious to people.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.78,0:14:06.58,Default,,0,0,0,,I mean, when they're really not very nice.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.57,0:14:10.27,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, I don't think it's difficult.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.27,0:14:11.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, that's you.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.85,0:14:17.59,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm striving towards that, David.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.59,0:14:18.91,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm trying to get there.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.91,0:14:19.79,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm sort of.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.79,0:14:25.11,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm feeling sorry for them if they're not having a better day.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.11,0:14:26.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.11,0:14:27.72,Default,,0,0,0,,God bless everyone.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.72,0:14:32.72,Default,,0,0,0,,And, you know, I always start out with that attitude in the day.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.72,0:14:33.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Mm-hmm.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.72,0:14:34.72,Default,,0,0,0,,God bless everyone.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.72,0:14:35.72,Default,,0,0,0,,And God bless the doggie.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.72,0:14:36.72,Default,,0,0,0,,And God bless the canary.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.72,0:14:41.72,Default,,0,0,0,,And God bless all of God's creation.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.72,0:14:42.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Mm-hmm.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.72,0:14:52.74,Default,,0,0,0,,You know, you want to become the kind of a person that your mere presence is beneficial
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.74,0:14:53.74,Default,,0,0,0,,to the world.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.74,0:14:54.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Mm-hmm.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.56,0:15:02.60,Default,,0,0,0,,What you have become then contributes and uplifts everyone.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.60,0:15:03.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.60,0:15:04.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.60,0:15:07.60,Default,,0,0,0,,So then that leads us a little bit into surrender.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.60,0:15:08.60,Default,,0,0,0,,All right.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.60,0:15:19.60,Default,,0,0,0,,So when you come up against a block, which I call someone who, you know, is rude or obnoxious,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.60,0:15:25.76,Default,,0,0,0,,so you have to surrender the fact that they may be having a bad day or you might have
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.76,0:15:26.76,Default,,0,0,0,,said something that upset them.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.76,0:15:28.76,Default,,0,0,0,,They need help, yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.76,0:15:29.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.76,0:15:33.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, that's a nice way of putting it but...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.11,0:15:39.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, when people are mean and nasty and awful, you know, I figure they really need help,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.18,0:15:40.18,Default,,0,0,0,,you see.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.18,0:15:41.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Mm-hmm.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.56,0:15:42.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.56,0:15:45.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Mm-hmm.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.74,0:15:46.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, they do.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.90,0:15:49.90,Default,,0,0,0,,And you can actually change them by sending them love.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.90,0:15:50.90,Default,,0,0,0,,That's what I wanted to know.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.90,0:15:51.90,Default,,0,0,0,,How do you change them?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.90,0:15:52.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Thinking of them lovingly.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.90,0:15:57.99,Default,,0,0,0,,You think of them lovingly and forgivingly and picture them at their very best.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.99,0:16:00.99,Default,,0,0,0,,And they hold that image of them.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.99,0:16:04.09,Default,,0,0,0,,And as you do that, you actually lift them.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.09,0:16:06.09,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's check the arm with this.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.09,0:16:08.09,Default,,0,0,0,,You actually do lift them.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.09,0:16:09.09,Default,,0,0,0,,Uh-huh.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.09,0:16:10.09,Default,,0,0,0,,You see?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.09,0:16:16.25,Default,,0,0,0,,You actually do lift them by seeing their positive values and their contribution to the world.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.25,0:16:22.50,Default,,0,0,0,,And I say to myself, well, I'm thankful that person is in the world.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.50,0:16:25.75,Default,,0,0,0,,And then it becomes a fact.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.75,0:16:26.75,Default,,0,0,0,,It becomes a fact.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.75,0:16:27.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Mm-hmm.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.75,0:16:35.85,Default,,0,0,0,,So the more loving we are, the more lovable people in society and the world become.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.85,0:16:40.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Mm-hmm.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.78,0:16:43.78,Default,,0,0,0,,So to love the world, then, is a major contribution.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.78,0:16:47.81,Default,,0,0,0,,Love the world and everyone in it.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.81,0:16:54.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, we have a lot of people that say, I want to change the world or I want to change
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.42,0:16:57.42,Default,,0,0,0,,this opinion.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.42,0:17:02.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Instead of looking at themselves to change, they want to change what's out there.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.42,0:17:04.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, that's the impact of the media.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.77,0:17:05.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Mm-hmm.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.77,0:17:12.41,Default,,0,0,0,,Of course, the media give a lot of people enormous power in the public.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.41,0:17:18.47,Default,,0,0,0,,So one little person expressing one little idea is now transmitted to millions of people
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.47,0:17:20.60,Default,,0,0,0,,and actually is changing them.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.60,0:17:21.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Mm-hmm.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.60,0:17:23.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Actually is changing them.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.60,0:17:24.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Mm-hmm.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.60,0:17:30.19,Default,,0,0,0,,We watch the news and how the news is handled.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.19,0:17:32.19,Default,,0,0,0,,He's already changing the news.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.19,0:17:33.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Mm-hmm.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.19,0:17:34.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Mm-hmm.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.19,0:17:35.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Mm-hmm.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.19,0:17:40.50,Default,,0,0,0,,So observing myself, does that change the world?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.50,0:17:48.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Observing yourself because you're becoming more self-aware makes you a more beneficial
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.08,0:17:51.21,Default,,0,0,0,,contributor to the world and society.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.21,0:17:58.27,Default,,0,0,0,,When you're aware of your own shortcomings, then you tend to override them and compensate
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.27,0:17:59.27,Default,,0,0,0,,for them.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.27,0:18:00.27,Default,,0,0,0,,Mm-hmm.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.27,0:18:04.27,Default,,0,0,0,,So instead of being a sourpuss, you try to put on a smiley face.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.27,0:18:05.27,Default,,0,0,0,,Mm-hmm.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.27,0:18:06.27,Default,,0,0,0,,Mm-hmm.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.27,0:18:07.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Mm-hmm.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.85,0:18:10.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Mm-hmm.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.16,0:18:11.16,Default,,0,0,0,,All right.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.16,0:18:22.37,Default,,0,0,0,,So is someone below 200 capable of inter-inventory?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.37,0:18:25.37,Default,,0,0,0,,I call it inter-inventory.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.37,0:18:28.37,Default,,0,0,0,,It's an inventory of my self.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.37,0:18:32.56,Default,,0,0,0,,So is someone below 200 capable of that?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.56,0:18:35.62,Default,,0,0,0,,I think in general, not really.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.62,0:18:40.20,Default,,0,0,0,,But with help, they can be taught how to be that way.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.20,0:18:46.26,Default,,0,0,0,,We have psychologists who interview prisoners, and many of them start out with absolutely
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.26,0:18:50.26,Default,,0,0,0,,zero insight or motivation.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.26,0:18:58.99,Default,,0,0,0,,But by interaction with that psychologist, who is personally loving and caring, the person
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.99,0:19:00.99,Default,,0,0,0,,becomes changed.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.99,0:19:07.12,Default,,0,0,0,,So without trying to change them, we change others by virtue of what we are and have become
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.12,0:19:10.12,Default,,0,0,0,,and the way we are with them.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.12,0:19:14.41,Default,,0,0,0,,We are already changing them without trying to change them.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.41,0:19:17.41,Default,,0,0,0,,If you try to change people, they resist.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.41,0:19:21.73,Default,,0,0,0,,So that's force, you know, like power and force.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.73,0:19:22.73,Default,,0,0,0,,That's right.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.73,0:19:27.34,Default,,0,0,0,,So just be considerate and loving and considerate.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.34,0:19:32.34,Default,,0,0,0,,There are a lot of individuals, however, that even under the most terrific conditions are
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.34,0:19:35.34,Default,,0,0,0,,unable to prove or show benefit.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.34,0:19:41.39,Default,,0,0,0,,And they seem to be of a very limited capability.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.39,0:19:48.68,Default,,0,0,0,,So in other words, we can't really force anyone to be different.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.68,0:19:56.78,Default,,0,0,0,,We just have to pray that they would someday realize their shortcomings?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.78,0:19:59.78,Default,,0,0,0,,We do all that we can on their behalf.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.78,0:20:02.78,Default,,0,0,0,,And we hold in mind their best interests.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.78,0:20:10.78,Default,,0,0,0,,And I picture the person as being what it is that I hold as an ideal.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.78,0:20:18.26,Default,,0,0,0,,I picture them as being more loving, more caring, more polite, more considerate.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.26,0:20:22.35,Default,,0,0,0,,And by doing that, I influence them to become that way.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.35,0:20:23.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Resist.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.35,0:20:24.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.35,0:20:25.35,Default,,0,0,0,,All right.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.35,0:20:30.35,Default,,0,0,0,,So merely picturing a person as more loving, more capable, more polite, more efficient,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.35,0:20:37.93,Default,,0,0,0,,more intelligent, whatever you want, already influences them because you're not trying
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.93,0:20:38.93,Default,,0,0,0,,to influence them.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.93,0:20:40.93,Default,,0,0,0,,So there's nothing for them to resist.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.93,0:20:46.31,Default,,0,0,0,,If you're trying to train them to become a different way, they now will resist that.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.31,0:20:48.31,Default,,0,0,0,,So I don't tell them what I'm doing.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:48.31,0:20:55.47,Default,,0,0,0,,I just hold in mind that this person is very lovable, capable of love, and polite, and
Dialogue: 0,0:20:55.47,0:20:58.47,Default,,0,0,0,,seems to be able to handle things.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:58.47,0:21:02.47,Default,,0,0,0,,And by holding that in mind, it actually becomes a fact.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:02.47,0:21:06.47,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, I know that you did that when you were in practice.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:06.47,0:21:09.47,Default,,0,0,0,,You would hold in mind that your patience got better.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:09.47,0:21:10.47,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:10.47,0:21:17.86,Default,,0,0,0,,And you can put that into different aspects of your life, and you're changing the world.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:17.86,0:21:18.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:18.86,0:21:19.86,Default,,0,0,0,,I did that as a psychiatrist.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:19.86,0:21:28.02,Default,,0,0,0,,I held in mind a picture of the person and how I felt they were capable of becoming friendly
Dialogue: 0,0:21:28.02,0:21:35.91,Default,,0,0,0,,instead of sour, and mild in manner instead of threatening, etc.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:35.91,0:21:40.07,Default,,0,0,0,,And they became that way.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:40.07,0:21:41.07,Default,,0,0,0,,They became that way.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:41.07,0:21:50.70,Default,,0,0,0,,And they themselves discovered that they were being influenced in that way.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:50.70,0:21:54.70,Default,,0,0,0,,I remember a couple of patients said they had a picture of me and they put it on the
Dialogue: 0,0:21:54.70,0:21:55.70,Default,,0,0,0,,wall.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:55.70,0:21:59.70,Default,,0,0,0,,And when they got into a bad mood or angry or paranoid or whatever, they would go over
Dialogue: 0,0:21:59.70,0:22:00.70,Default,,0,0,0,,and look at my picture.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:00.70,0:22:03.70,Default,,0,0,0,,And right away, they would feel better.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:03.70,0:22:11.12,Default,,0,0,0,,That made me happy that just one image could be beneficial.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:11.12,0:22:14.12,Default,,0,0,0,,It made people more grateful to be alive and appreciated.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:14.12,0:22:16.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, I tended to love all my patients.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:16.82,0:22:18.82,Default,,0,0,0,,I didn't tell them that, of course.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:18.82,0:22:24.39,Default,,0,0,0,,But I tended to love them all.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:24.39,0:22:26.39,Default,,0,0,0,,And that played a big part in their getting better.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:26.39,0:22:27.39,Default,,0,0,0,,Resist.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:27.39,0:22:28.49,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:28.49,0:22:33.71,Default,,0,0,0,,So the reason I had a high recovery rate is because I loved them all.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:33.71,0:22:35.71,Default,,0,0,0,,I wouldn't dare tell them that.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:35.71,0:22:36.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Of course not.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:36.71,0:22:41.90,Default,,0,0,0,,But I used to pray for them and send them love and best wishes.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:41.90,0:22:48.51,Default,,0,0,0,,And picture their best interests, hold their best interests in mind.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:48.51,0:22:51.51,Default,,0,0,0,,And then that would come to pass.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:51.51,0:22:53.51,Default,,0,0,0,,That would come to pass.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:53.51,0:23:01.63,Default,,0,0,0,,So we do the same thing in our personal lives without being necessarily a professional doing
Dialogue: 0,0:23:01.63,0:23:06.08,Default,,0,0,0,,it, some kind of a professional level.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:06.08,0:23:08.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Just on a personal level.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:08.40,0:23:12.40,Default,,0,0,0,,We picture the people we love in the highest level that we can picture them.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:12.40,0:23:14.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Happy and content and satisfied.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:14.40,0:23:17.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Doing well in school and whatever it is.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:17.40,0:23:20.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Getting promotions at work.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:20.78,0:23:29.36,Default,,0,0,0,,So if you were, let's say in our daily work lives, you know, we try and do the very best
Dialogue: 0,0:23:29.36,0:23:34.36,Default,,0,0,0,,we possibly can at the job that we are doing.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:34.36,0:23:36.36,Default,,0,0,0,,So we try and do the very best.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:36.36,0:23:44.65,Default,,0,0,0,,I have found that if you do that and you put in just a little extra effort, that it's usually
Dialogue: 0,0:23:44.65,0:23:45.65,Default,,0,0,0,,recognized.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:45.65,0:23:47.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:47.19,0:23:48.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Even a little bit of effort.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:48.19,0:23:52.19,Default,,0,0,0,,People say, well, that couldn't make any difference that you said thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:52.19,0:23:53.19,Default,,0,0,0,,It does.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:53.19,0:24:01.19,Default,,0,0,0,,So when you thank the clerk, thank you for taking care of me at the cash register or
Dialogue: 0,0:24:01.19,0:24:02.26,Default,,0,0,0,,whatever.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:02.26,0:24:05.26,Default,,0,0,0,,When you say thank you, you've changed their day.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:05.26,0:24:07.67,Default,,0,0,0,,You've changed their life.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:07.67,0:24:11.67,Default,,0,0,0,,So every thank you is a blessing in disguise.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:11.67,0:24:15.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Every thank you is a blessing in disguise.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:15.25,0:24:23.72,Default,,0,0,0,,So we make our life thankful to all the people around us who make our life possible.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:23.72,0:24:32.16,Default,,0,0,0,,If it wasn't for the people in the room right now, we wouldn't be able to be speaking and
Dialogue: 0,0:24:32.16,0:24:34.16,Default,,0,0,0,,interviewing and recording this.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:34.16,0:24:40.32,Default,,0,0,0,,So I'm grateful to all the people that are in the room right now without whom we would
Dialogue: 0,0:24:40.32,0:24:43.32,Default,,0,0,0,,not be able to be having this interview.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:43.32,0:24:44.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:44.32,0:24:45.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Dum ta dum dum.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:45.32,0:24:46.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Dum ta dum dum.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:46.32,0:24:47.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Dum ta dum dum.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:47.32,0:24:48.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Our bird says that now.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:48.32,0:24:49.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Dum ta dum dum.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:49.32,0:24:54.32,Default,,0,0,0,,And I always look for Dave in the room when she's saying it.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:54.32,0:24:55.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Dum ta dum dum.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:55.32,0:24:56.32,Default,,0,0,0,,It's cute.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:56.32,0:25:10.89,Default,,0,0,0,,So now that we have taken an inventory of ourselves, how do we correct things when,
Dialogue: 0,0:25:10.89,0:25:14.89,Default,,0,0,0,,you know, it's like a knee-jerk reaction when something happens.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:14.89,0:25:16.89,Default,,0,0,0,,So how do we not respond?
Dialogue: 0,0:25:16.89,0:25:25.89,Default,,0,0,0,,How do we not respond in that knee-jerk reaction since, you know, to lose our temper or do
Dialogue: 0,0:25:25.89,0:25:27.89,Default,,0,0,0,,we pray to see things differently?
Dialogue: 0,0:25:27.89,0:25:30.89,Default,,0,0,0,,Do we, how do you train yourself not to do that?
Dialogue: 0,0:25:30.89,0:25:32.89,Default,,0,0,0,,I think we do all those things.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:32.89,0:25:35.92,Default,,0,0,0,,We train ourselves to see differently.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:35.92,0:25:40.92,Default,,0,0,0,,We ask, we pray to God and ask for help to bring about a change.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:40.92,0:25:42.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:42.08,0:25:47.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Accept and surrender to the things we cannot change and encourage to change the things
Dialogue: 0,0:25:47.21,0:25:48.21,Default,,0,0,0,,we can.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:48.21,0:25:49.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Right.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:49.21,0:25:50.21,Default,,0,0,0,,It's part of the 12-step movement, yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:50.21,0:25:57.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Pray for knowledge of your will for us and the power to change what we can.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:57.75,0:26:08.67,Default,,0,0,0,,So by changing one's shortcomings in ourselves, that's what really changes the world.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:08.67,0:26:10.67,Default,,0,0,0,,That's what changes the world.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:10.67,0:26:16.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Every little gesture that you can change in yourself reverberates throughout the world.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:16.67,0:26:17.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:17.67,0:26:22.99,Default,,0,0,0,,As unlikely as that may seem to reason, but we're not dealing with reason.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:22.99,0:26:30.15,Default,,0,0,0,,We're dealing with energies within the field of consciousness itself, which is a different
Dialogue: 0,0:26:30.15,0:26:31.15,Default,,0,0,0,,realm.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:31.15,0:26:34.47,Default,,0,0,0,,The physical world is one realm.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:34.47,0:26:39.47,Default,,0,0,0,,The vibrational energies in the field of consciousness is a different realm, yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:39.47,0:26:48.87,Default,,0,0,0,,We change the world by what we have become and who we are and we thereby become a blessing
Dialogue: 0,0:26:48.87,0:26:49.87,Default,,0,0,0,,to the world.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:49.87,0:26:51.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Instead of bad news.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:51.00,0:26:52.00,Default,,0,0,0,,But you didn't answer my question.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:52.00,0:27:03.13,Default,,0,0,0,,How do you change the knee-jerk reaction where you want to, you know, you know, how do you
Dialogue: 0,0:27:03.13,0:27:05.13,Default,,0,0,0,,change that reaction?
Dialogue: 0,0:27:05.13,0:27:08.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, by conscious awareness you already change it.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:08.26,0:27:14.26,Default,,0,0,0,,By conscious awareness is the only way I know it from a practical viewpoint.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:14.26,0:27:15.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:15.35,0:27:19.35,Default,,0,0,0,,By awareness that you're short-tempered you automatically become more even.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:19.35,0:27:26.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Evenly tempered because you're now aware that that is a shortcoming in yourself.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:26.45,0:27:31.45,Default,,0,0,0,,So you bite your tongue and don't say anything.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:31.45,0:27:32.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Right?
Dialogue: 0,0:27:32.67,0:27:33.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:33.67,0:27:38.86,Default,,0,0,0,,So you do what you can to become as perfect as you're capable of doing and that way you
Dialogue: 0,0:27:38.86,0:27:41.86,Default,,0,0,0,,improve everyone around you, including yourself.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:41.86,0:27:42.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:42.86,0:27:44.15,Default,,0,0,0,,The world benefits.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:44.15,0:27:47.44,Default,,0,0,0,,The whole world benefits by your efforts.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:47.44,0:27:48.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Mm-hmm.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:48.44,0:27:54.62,Default,,0,0,0,,That way you become a blessing to the world instead of bad news.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:54.62,0:27:59.62,Default,,0,0,0,,And you lift the ships that are in the water.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:59.62,0:28:01.62,Default,,0,0,0,,That's very good, yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:01.62,0:28:04.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Wow.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:04.06,0:28:10.14,Default,,0,0,0,,But everyone thinks that they have to lift the whole ocean instead of just lifting one
Dialogue: 0,0:28:10.14,0:28:11.14,Default,,0,0,0,,ship.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:11.14,0:28:16.14,Default,,0,0,0,,If you just lift one ship, isn't that ... I mean, everyone wants to save the world, you
Dialogue: 0,0:28:16.14,0:28:19.35,Default,,0,0,0,,know.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:19.35,0:28:24.35,Default,,0,0,0,,So anyway, we all become more realistic the older we get.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:24.35,0:28:34.80,Default,,0,0,0,,We all become more realistic and we are satisfied with having less of an impact.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:34.80,0:28:44.34,Default,,0,0,0,,In other words, the less your own ego is involved, the better because you don't have to be a major
Dialogue: 0,0:28:44.34,0:28:49.34,Default,,0,0,0,,star on television in order to be of value to the world.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:49.34,0:28:57.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Really being more kindly and gentle and polite, considerate.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:57.28,0:28:58.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Mm-hmm.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:58.28,0:29:09.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Would you say that if we followed this and really did a self-inventory and tried to change
Dialogue: 0,0:29:09.28,0:29:14.44,Default,,0,0,0,,ourselves, that would actually work to change the world?
Dialogue: 0,0:29:14.44,0:29:16.44,Default,,0,0,0,,That actually changes the world, yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:16.44,0:29:19.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Changing yourself actually changes the world.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:19.44,0:29:21.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Mm-hmm.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:21.18,0:29:28.97,Default,,0,0,0,,The world is not the same if you're polite today.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:28.97,0:29:32.00,Default,,0,0,0,,We benefit the world by what we have become.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:32.00,0:29:38.00,Default,,0,0,0,,And what we have become is based on our intention and our values that we have integrated and
Dialogue: 0,0:29:38.00,0:29:42.26,Default,,0,0,0,,made part of our own self-image.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:42.26,0:29:44.31,Default,,0,0,0,,Mm-hmm.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:44.31,0:29:50.58,Default,,0,0,0,,So, you know, we're dealing in a very ...
Dialogue: 0,0:29:50.58,0:29:51.58,Default,,0,0,0,,...
Dialogue: 0,0:29:51.58,0:29:52.58,Default,,0,0,0,,...
Dialogue: 0,0:29:52.58,0:29:53.68,Default,,0,0,0,,...
Dialogue: 0,0:29:53.68,0:29:54.68,Default,,0,0,0,,...
Dialogue: 0,0:29:54.68,0:29:55.68,Default,,0,0,0,,...
Dialogue: 0,0:29:55.68,0:29:56.68,Default,,0,0,0,,...
Dialogue: 0,0:29:56.68,0:29:57.68,Default,,0,0,0,,...
Dialogue: 0,0:29:57.68,0:29:58.68,Default,,0,0,0,,...
Dialogue: 0,0:29:58.68,0:29:59.68,Default,,0,0,0,,...
Dialogue: 0,0:29:59.68,0:30:00.68,Default,,0,0,0,,...
Dialogue: 0,0:30:00.68,0:30:01.68,Default,,0,0,0,,...
Dialogue: 0,0:30:01.68,0:30:02.68,Default,,0,0,0,,...
Dialogue: 0,0:30:02.68,0:30:03.68,Default,,0,0,0,,...
Dialogue: 0,0:30:03.68,0:30:04.68,Default,,0,0,0,,...
Dialogue: 0,0:30:04.68,0:30:05.68,Default,,0,0,0,,...
Dialogue: 0,0:30:05.68,0:30:06.68,Default,,0,0,0,,...
Dialogue: 0,0:30:06.68,0:30:07.68,Default,,0,0,0,,...
Dialogue: 0,0:30:07.68,0:30:08.68,Default,,0,0,0,,...
Dialogue: 0,0:30:08.68,0:30:09.68,Default,,0,0,0,,...
Dialogue: 0,0:30:09.68,0:30:10.68,Default,,0,0,0,,...
Dialogue: 0,0:30:10.68,0:30:11.68,Default,,0,0,0,,...
Dialogue: 0,0:30:11.68,0:30:12.68,Default,,0,0,0,,...
Dialogue: 0,0:30:12.68,0:30:13.68,Default,,0,0,0,,...
Dialogue: 0,0:30:13.68,0:30:14.68,Default,,0,0,0,,...
