Dialogue: 0,0:30:16.29,0:30:17.29,Default,,0,0,0,,...
Dialogue: 0,0:30:17.29,0:30:18.29,Default,,0,0,0,,...
Dialogue: 0,0:30:18.29,0:30:19.80,Default,,0,0,0,,...
Dialogue: 0,0:30:19.80,0:30:20.80,Default,,0,0,0,,...
Dialogue: 0,0:30:20.80,0:30:21.80,Default,,0,0,0,,...
Dialogue: 0,0:30:21.80,0:30:22.80,Default,,0,0,0,,...
Dialogue: 0,0:30:22.80,0:30:23.80,Default,,0,0,0,,...
Dialogue: 0,0:30:23.80,0:30:24.80,Default,,0,0,0,,...
Dialogue: 0,0:30:24.80,0:30:25.80,Default,,0,0,0,,...
Dialogue: 0,0:30:25.80,0:30:26.80,Default,,0,0,0,,...
Dialogue: 0,0:30:26.80,0:30:27.80,Default,,0,0,0,,...
Dialogue: 0,0:30:27.80,0:30:28.80,Default,,0,0,0,,...
Dialogue: 0,0:30:28.80,0:30:29.80,Default,,0,0,0,,...
Dialogue: 0,0:30:29.80,0:30:30.80,Default,,0,0,0,,...
Dialogue: 0,0:30:30.80,0:30:31.80,Default,,0,0,0,,...
Dialogue: 0,0:30:31.80,0:30:41.80,Default,,0,0,0,,This is a question I have from someone.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:41.80,0:30:48.96,Default,,0,0,0,,When a person lies, does that affect the efforts they have, wait, let me see.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:48.96,0:30:49.96,Default,,0,0,0,,The effect.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:49.96,0:30:50.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:50.96,0:30:55.71,Default,,0,0,0,,What effect does that have when a person lies?
Dialogue: 0,0:30:55.71,0:31:06.00,Default,,0,0,0,,It throws a negative energy into a field and can be quite disruptive, and therefore I advise
Dialogue: 0,0:31:06.00,0:31:11.85,Default,,0,0,0,,people to avoid it at all costs if possible, because it's often self-defeating.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:11.85,0:31:12.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:12.85,0:31:13.85,Default,,0,0,0,,It's self-defeating.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:13.85,0:31:17.98,Default,,0,0,0,,So lying would be considered what, below 200?
Dialogue: 0,0:31:17.98,0:31:18.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:18.98,0:31:20.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Mm-hmm.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:20.68,0:31:21.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Right.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:21.68,0:31:22.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Mm-hmm.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:22.68,0:31:24.80,Default,,0,0,0,,It's self-defeating.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:24.80,0:31:25.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Mm-hmm.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:25.80,0:31:28.22,Default,,0,0,0,,And does that affect who you are?
Dialogue: 0,0:31:28.22,0:31:33.84,Default,,0,0,0,,When you lie or tell little, sometimes little white lies are to protect people, you know
Dialogue: 0,0:31:33.84,0:31:35.54,Default,,0,0,0,,what I mean.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:35.54,0:31:39.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Sometimes little white lies are to help people, you know, you don't want to hurt their feelings
Dialogue: 0,0:31:39.62,0:31:41.52,Default,,0,0,0,,so you say a little white lie.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:41.52,0:31:46.60,Default,,0,0,0,,But when you're doing it maliciously, you know, does that?
Dialogue: 0,0:31:46.60,0:31:47.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:47.60,0:31:50.34,Default,,0,0,0,,So the intention gives it the energy field.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:50.34,0:31:51.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:51.34,0:31:59.26,Default,,0,0,0,,It isn't just the facts, it's the intention and the whole energy of the surrounding to
Dialogue: 0,0:31:59.26,0:31:59.38,Default,,0,0,0,,the reality.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:59.46,0:32:00.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Mm-hmm.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:00.46,0:32:02.23,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:02.23,0:32:03.23,Default,,0,0,0,,That's what I'm saying.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:03.23,0:32:04.23,Default,,0,0,0,,That's what I'm saying.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:04.23,0:32:05.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Mm-hmm.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:05.84,0:32:06.84,Default,,0,0,0,,That's what I'm saying.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:06.84,0:32:07.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Mm-hmm.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:07.84,0:32:08.84,Default,,0,0,0,,But does that affect who you are?
Dialogue: 0,0:32:08.84,0:32:09.84,Default,,0,0,0,,When you tell a lie or a little white lie or whatever.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:09.84,0:32:10.84,Default,,0,0,0,,That affects who you are.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:10.84,0:32:11.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, indeed it does.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:11.84,0:32:12.84,Default,,0,0,0,,It does tell who, it does affect you.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:12.84,0:32:13.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, it does have a deleterious effect.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:13.84,0:32:14.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Mm-hmm.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:14.84,0:32:15.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, that isn't what I wanted to hear.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:15.84,0:32:17.26,Default,,0,0,0,,What you're asking is how can you get, be evil and get away with it.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:17.26,0:32:18.26,Default,,0,0,0,,No.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:18.26,0:32:19.26,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm just saying, no, I'm just saying, yeah, well, yes, I guess I'm saying that.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:19.26,0:32:20.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:20.29,0:32:21.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:21.29,0:32:22.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:22.29,0:32:23.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:23.29,0:32:24.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:24.29,0:32:25.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:25.29,0:32:26.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:26.29,0:32:27.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:27.29,0:32:28.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:28.29,0:32:32.22,Default,,0,0,0,,I mean, yeah, well, yes, I guess I am.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:33.22,0:32:35.22,Default,,0,0,0,,You know, I guess there is a-
Dialogue: 0,0:32:35.22,0:32:36.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Not evil, but you know-
Dialogue: 0,0:32:36.22,0:32:37.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, I-
Dialogue: 0,0:32:37.22,0:32:38.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Less than ideal, let's say.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:38.22,0:32:39.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:39.22,0:32:40.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:40.22,0:32:55.26,Default,,0,0,0,,So, if you, if you were, how do I say, people that are above 200, they still can lie.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:55.26,0:32:56.49,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, uh-huh.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:56.49,0:32:57.49,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:57.49,0:33:02.58,Default,,0,0,0,,I mean, so, so, I mean, but they do it with a conscience.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:04.22,0:33:05.22,Default,,0,0,0,,They feel guilty about it.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:05.22,0:33:06.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:06.22,0:33:07.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:07.22,0:33:08.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Because if they're under 200, they don't feel guilty about it.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:08.22,0:33:09.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Right.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:09.22,0:33:13.22,Default,,0,0,0,,So, you know, but they can, they still have the capabilities to lie, even though they're
Dialogue: 0,0:33:13.22,0:33:14.22,Default,,0,0,0,,above 200.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:14.22,0:33:18.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, yes, but it's a different affair.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:18.38,0:33:19.38,Default,,0,0,0,,All right.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:19.38,0:33:22.38,Default,,0,0,0,,It's a different affair to be conscious of what you're doing-
Dialogue: 0,0:33:22.38,0:33:23.38,Default,,0,0,0,,And not conscious.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:23.38,0:33:24.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Or oblivious, yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:24.38,0:33:25.38,Default,,0,0,0,,All right.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:25.38,0:33:26.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Mm-hmm.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:26.70,0:33:27.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:27.70,0:33:28.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, that explains a lot.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:28.70,0:33:33.07,Default,,0,0,0,,I mean, because that, that explains a lot.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:33.07,0:33:34.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, indeed.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:34.07,0:33:39.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Why people, you know, just because they're above 200 doesn't mean they still can't do
Dialogue: 0,0:33:39.07,0:33:40.14,Default,,0,0,0,,something wrong.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:40.14,0:33:41.14,Default,,0,0,0,,They can still do.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:41.14,0:33:42.14,Default,,0,0,0,,They're not, well, they're not holy.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:42.14,0:33:43.33,Default,,0,0,0,,They're not, you know-
Dialogue: 0,0:33:43.33,0:33:44.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:44.33,0:33:45.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Right.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:45.33,0:33:46.33,Default,,0,0,0,,They aren't Christ-like.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:46.33,0:33:47.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Right.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:47.33,0:33:48.33,Default,,0,0,0,,You know.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:48.33,0:33:49.33,Default,,0,0,0,,But they're not really below 200, even though they-
Dialogue: 0,0:33:49.33,0:33:50.90,Default,,0,0,0,,No.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:50.90,0:33:51.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:51.90,0:33:52.90,Default,,0,0,0,,So, the wide range that includes most people is between 200 and, and the higher numbers,
Dialogue: 0,0:33:52.90,0:33:53.90,Default,,0,0,0,,you know.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:53.90,0:33:54.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Mm-hmm.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:54.90,0:33:55.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Somewhere in between.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:55.90,0:33:56.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, we know that the 300 level is usually service, you know, to others.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:56.90,0:33:57.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Uh-huh.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:57.90,0:33:58.90,Default,,0,0,0,,300.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:58.90,0:33:59.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Mm-hmm.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:59.90,0:34:00.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:00.90,0:34:01.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Mm-hmm.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:01.90,0:34:02.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:02.90,0:34:03.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Mm-hmm.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:03.90,0:34:04.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Mm-hmm.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:04.90,0:34:05.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Mm-hmm.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:05.90,0:34:06.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Mm-hmm.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:06.90,0:34:07.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Mm-hmm.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:07.90,0:34:08.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Mm-hmm.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:08.90,0:34:09.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Mm-hmm.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:09.90,0:34:10.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Mm-hmm.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:10.90,0:34:13.90,Default,,0,0,0,,And the 300, anyone in the 300 range is usually service to others.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:13.90,0:34:14.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:14.90,0:34:15.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Uh-huh.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:15.90,0:34:19.58,Default,,0,0,0,,And they usually do service type work, whether it's plumbing, construction-
Dialogue: 0,0:34:19.58,0:34:20.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Or service towards their families.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:20.58,0:34:21.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Towards their families.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:21.58,0:34:22.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Not necessarily occupation.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:22.58,0:34:23.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Right.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:23.58,0:34:24.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Right.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:24.58,0:34:25.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Mm-hmm.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:25.58,0:34:26.58,Default,,0,0,0,,But, I mean, they are of service to other people.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:26.58,0:34:28.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Just by who they are, yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:28.58,0:34:29.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:29.58,0:34:30.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Mm-hmm.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:30.58,0:34:31.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Right.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:31.58,0:34:33.58,Default,,0,0,0,,And then the 400's is usually the intellect.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:33.58,0:34:35.58,Default,,0,0,0,,The intellect comes in more strongly.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:35.58,0:34:36.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Right.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:36.58,0:34:37.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Mm-hmm.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:37.58,0:34:38.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Right.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:38.58,0:34:39.58,Default,,0,0,0,,And the 500's is usually loving.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:39.58,0:34:40.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Right.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:40.58,0:34:46.58,Default,,0,0,0,,They're in the, they want to be 540, which is unconditional love.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:46.58,0:34:49.58,Default,,0,0,0,,But unconditional love is really hard to reach.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:49.58,0:34:56.58,Default,,0,0,0,,And so many people are saying that they're, at least from emails I get, that they are
Dialogue: 0,0:34:56.58,0:34:59.64,Default,,0,0,0,,in the 540's, which-
Dialogue: 0,0:34:59.64,0:35:01.64,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't know anybody that says that.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:01.64,0:35:02.64,Default,,0,0,0,,I do.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:02.64,0:35:03.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:04.64,0:35:09.90,Default,,0,0,0,,And yet they're not, because their actions aren't there.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:09.90,0:35:14.34,Default,,0,0,0,,The person themselves are not there.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:14.34,0:35:19.34,Default,,0,0,0,,If you're really loving, you don't really care what your calibration is, you know what
Dialogue: 0,0:35:19.34,0:35:20.34,Default,,0,0,0,,I mean?
Dialogue: 0,0:35:20.34,0:35:21.34,Default,,0,0,0,,It's just sort of an academic-
Dialogue: 0,0:35:21.34,0:35:22.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:22.34,0:35:24.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Academic curiosity, but it's not really important.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:24.34,0:35:25.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:25.34,0:35:26.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:26.34,0:35:29.34,Default,,0,0,0,,It's not going to make anybody happy, the fact that you calibrated 540.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:29.34,0:35:30.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Right.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:30.34,0:35:35.34,Default,,0,0,0,,The fact that you made them a peanut butter sandwich is going to carry a lot more weight.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:35.34,0:35:36.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:36.82,0:35:37.82,Default,,0,0,0,,So, if we, let's say that-
Dialogue: 0,0:35:37.82,0:35:39.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:39.21,0:35:40.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:40.21,0:35:50.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's say that we are in the 300's and we want to make it to the 500's.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:50.17,0:35:51.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Can you skip levels?
Dialogue: 0,0:35:51.17,0:35:54.65,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't know, I've never asked that question.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:54.65,0:35:55.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:55.65,0:36:01.65,Default,,0,0,0,,I would imagine a major decision, you know, you live a certain way and you come into a
Dialogue: 0,0:36:01.65,0:36:03.65,Default,,0,0,0,,crisis and now you make a major change.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:03.65,0:36:09.71,Default,,0,0,0,,I imagine you could make that decision in a matter of seconds, to be generous or not
Dialogue: 0,0:36:09.71,0:36:10.71,Default,,0,0,0,,generous.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:10.71,0:36:11.71,Default,,0,0,0,,To retaliate or not retaliate.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:11.71,0:36:12.71,Default,,0,0,0,,To choose love instead of hate, that's a fast decision.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:12.71,0:36:13.71,Default,,0,0,0,,So, in other words, some knee-jerk reactions are good.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:13.71,0:36:14.71,Default,,0,0,0,,They don't always have to be bad.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:14.71,0:36:16.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, they're not necessarily bad, no.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:16.42,0:36:17.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Very often they're a good impulse.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:17.42,0:36:18.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:18.42,0:36:19.42,Default,,0,0,0,,So, in changing what you are, changes the world.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:19.42,0:36:20.42,Default,,0,0,0,,What you are changes the world, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:36:20.42,0:36:21.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:21.61,0:36:22.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:22.61,0:36:23.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:23.61,0:36:24.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:24.61,0:36:25.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:25.61,0:36:26.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:26.61,0:36:27.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:27.61,0:36:28.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:28.61,0:36:29.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:29.61,0:36:30.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:30.61,0:36:31.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:31.61,0:36:32.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:32.61,0:36:33.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:33.61,0:36:35.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:35.18,0:36:38.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:38.55,0:36:39.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:39.55,0:36:40.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:40.55,0:36:41.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:41.55,0:36:42.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:42.55,0:36:43.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:43.55,0:36:44.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:44.55,0:36:45.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:45.55,0:36:46.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:46.55,0:36:47.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:47.55,0:36:48.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:48.55,0:36:49.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:49.55,0:36:50.81,Default,,0,0,0,,It changes the world.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:50.81,0:36:51.81,Default,,0,0,0,,So, how would you say we should live that in our everyday life?
Dialogue: 0,0:36:51.81,0:36:58.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Every incense of every day, your behavior and the way you are experiencing the world
Dialogue: 0,0:36:58.03,0:37:02.31,Default,,0,0,0,,is being influenced by your level of consciousness all the time.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:02.31,0:37:09.75,Default,,0,0,0,,It's either you are not thinking about it as a clinical fact, but it is an existential
Dialogue: 0,0:37:09.75,0:37:15.04,Default,,0,0,0,,fact, that at all times you're influencing what's around you unwittingly.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:15.04,0:37:15.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Absolutely.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:15.54,0:37:17.22,Default,,0,0,0,,either wittingly or unwittingly.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:18.16,0:37:20.50,Default,,0,0,0,,The more advanced you are in your own level of consciousness,
Dialogue: 0,0:37:20.76,0:37:24.55,Default,,0,0,0,,the more you become aware of what your influence is
Dialogue: 0,0:37:24.55,0:37:26.39,Default,,0,0,0,,on the world around you.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:27.51,0:37:29.60,Default,,0,0,0,,And you stop blaming the world.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:30.47,0:37:32.99,Default,,0,0,0,,If the world seems a little less than perfect today,
Dialogue: 0,0:37:35.26,0:37:38.72,Default,,0,0,0,,you stop being critical about that.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:39.36,0:37:41.50,Default,,0,0,0,,I mean, that's the limitation of the human existence.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:44.13,0:37:47.99,Default,,0,0,0,,The limitation of human existence itself is intrinsic.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:47.99,0:37:52.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Psychological, emotional, sociologically,
Dialogue: 0,0:37:53.38,0:37:55.42,Default,,0,0,0,,financially, educationally,
Dialogue: 0,0:37:56.00,0:38:01.37,Default,,0,0,0,,all these facets contribute then to the effective totality
Dialogue: 0,0:38:01.37,0:38:03.93,Default,,0,0,0,,of who we are and how we affect the world.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:06.20,0:38:09.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Some people lift the level of vibration of everyone in the room
Dialogue: 0,0:38:09.36,0:38:13.80,Default,,0,0,0,,by merely walking into the room, their mere presence.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:16.26,0:38:18.00,Default,,0,0,0,,In the party circuit, this is known,
Dialogue: 0,0:38:18.14,0:38:20.44,Default,,0,0,0,,certain people, if you immediately have them at your party,
Dialogue: 0,0:38:20.44,0:38:21.44,Default,,0,0,0,,it's going to be successful.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:21.48,0:38:24.38,Default,,0,0,0,,All you have to do is have them at your party
Dialogue: 0,0:38:24.38,0:38:25.48,Default,,0,0,0,,and that's all that's necessary.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:26.74,0:38:31.42,Default,,0,0,0,,That's how people vie to invite people of that nature.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:33.04,0:38:36.82,Default,,0,0,0,,They radiate a certain energy that uplifts everybody in the room.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:39.37,0:38:41.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Certain people are invited to your party,
Dialogue: 0,0:38:41.37,0:38:42.81,Default,,0,0,0,,the party will be a success.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:44.91,0:38:46.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Is that what you call a party animal?
Dialogue: 0,0:38:48.59,0:38:50.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, that's something different.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:50.03,0:38:50.15,Default,,0,0,0,,That's something different.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:53.17,0:38:56.55,Default,,0,0,0,,No, there are people that are truly, truly beneficial
Dialogue: 0,0:38:56.55,0:39:01.67,Default,,0,0,0,,to any collection of people together.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:02.97,0:39:04.95,Default,,0,0,0,,They have an uplifting effect on others.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:06.01,0:39:09.10,Default,,0,0,0,,So that's what we all strive to be within ourselves,
Dialogue: 0,0:39:09.34,0:39:13.25,Default,,0,0,0,,to be of such a nature that merely your presence
Dialogue: 0,0:39:13.25,0:39:15.73,Default,,0,0,0,,is uplifting to everyone in the room
Dialogue: 0,0:39:15.73,0:39:19.41,Default,,0,0,0,,and to the benefit of the humanity itself.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:19.41,0:39:19.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:21.15,0:39:23.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Kindliness and gentleness and lovingness.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:24.13,0:39:28.38,Default,,0,0,0,,See, even a dog can tell that difference.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:28.62,0:39:34.30,Default,,0,0,0,,A dog senses right away a loving, caring, gentle, safe person
Dialogue: 0,0:39:34.30,0:39:37.98,Default,,0,0,0,,and it senses one that is not fulfilled above.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:39.22,0:39:42.02,Default,,0,0,0,,It's more on guard and it keeps one eye open
Dialogue: 0,0:39:42.02,0:39:43.72,Default,,0,0,0,,and keeps an eye on you.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:45.14,0:39:48.84,Default,,0,0,0,,The dog keeps an eye on you.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:49.14,0:39:50.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Better watch what you're up to.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:52.70,0:39:58.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Would you say that when Jesus died for us,
Dialogue: 0,0:39:58.26,0:40:00.28,Default,,0,0,0,,our sins on the cross,
Dialogue: 0,0:40:00.84,0:40:02.67,Default,,0,0,0,,or, yes,
Dialogue: 0,0:40:03.21,0:40:06.57,Default,,0,0,0,,when Jesus died on the cross for our sins,
Dialogue: 0,0:40:07.45,0:40:13.21,Default,,0,0,0,,would you say that that was the time that the world changed?
Dialogue: 0,0:40:13.43,0:40:16.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Would that be, by him dying on the cross,
Dialogue: 0,0:40:16.25,0:40:21.07,Default,,0,0,0,,do you think that he actually, you know, he was a savior?
Dialogue: 0,0:40:21.07,0:40:24.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Historically, it is stated as such, yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:24.33,0:40:24.69,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:25.05,0:40:26.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Died as the savior of mankind.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:27.33,0:40:27.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:28.68,0:40:28.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:28.98,0:40:35.78,Default,,0,0,0,,So, at that time, he did help to elevate the world by his demise?
Dialogue: 0,0:40:36.70,0:40:38.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Profoundly, his sacrifice.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:39.97,0:40:42.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Because you wouldn't have salvation without...
Dialogue: 0,0:40:42.65,0:40:43.73,Default,,0,0,0,,There we are, yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:44.86,0:40:48.28,Default,,0,0,0,,I mean, you've stated that Jesus died for our salvation.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:48.46,0:40:48.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:50.26,0:40:55.51,Default,,0,0,0,,That's why he is Jesus the Christ.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:57.30,0:41:04.58,Default,,0,0,0,,So, we're all grateful as Christians
Dialogue: 0,0:41:04.58,0:41:07.31,Default,,0,0,0,,for the sacrifice.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:07.33,0:41:09.73,Default,,0,0,0,,For the sacrifice of Jesus Christ on behalf of mankind.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:10.41,0:41:13.61,Default,,0,0,0,,On behalf of mankind itself.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:16.23,0:41:16.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:19.77,0:41:22.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Is a person's consciousness,
Dialogue: 0,0:41:24.04,0:41:25.46,Default,,0,0,0,,does that affect,
Dialogue: 0,0:41:26.46,0:41:31.18,Default,,0,0,0,,what effect does that have on the world?
Dialogue: 0,0:41:31.84,0:41:34.06,Default,,0,0,0,,One's personal consciousness.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:34.58,0:41:36.94,Default,,0,0,0,,What would that effect be on the world?
Dialogue: 0,0:41:37.66,0:41:39.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, we sort of answered that.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:39.36,0:41:40.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, we did.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:40.06,0:41:40.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:40.18,0:41:40.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:40.22,0:41:40.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:40.26,0:41:40.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:40.28,0:41:40.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:40.30,0:41:40.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:40.32,0:41:40.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:40.34,0:41:40.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:40.36,0:41:40.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:40.40,0:41:40.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:40.42,0:41:40.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:40.48,0:41:40.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:40.54,0:41:40.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:40.64,0:41:40.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:40.70,0:41:40.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:40.76,0:41:40.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:40.86,0:41:40.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:40.88,0:41:40.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:40.94,0:41:41.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:41.04,0:41:41.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:41.18,0:41:41.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:41.24,0:41:41.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:41.26,0:41:41.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:41.28,0:41:41.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:41.46,0:41:42.80,Default,,0,0,0,,The more people you have interaction with.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:44.06,0:41:44.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:44.88,0:41:46.46,Default,,0,0,0,,The more people you have interaction with.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:47.51,0:41:50.49,Default,,0,0,0,,So, a miserable person living all alone
Dialogue: 0,0:41:50.49,0:41:53.73,Default,,0,0,0,,is going to have less effect than a miserable person
Dialogue: 0,0:41:53.73,0:41:56.25,Default,,0,0,0,,who is a major television personality.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:58.12,0:42:00.76,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm trying to look and see if there's any questions
Dialogue: 0,0:42:00.76,0:42:02.26,Default,,0,0,0,,that I need to...
Dialogue: 0,0:42:02.26,0:42:04.06,Default,,0,0,0,,that I have here.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:04.34,0:42:04.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Give me a minute.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:09.15,0:42:11.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay, here's a good one.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:11.94,0:42:14.24,Default,,0,0,0,,How do I change what I am?
Dialogue: 0,0:42:14.56,0:42:26.20,Default,,0,0,0,,what you are cannot be changed okay how you are what you are can be changed okay so so what i am
Dialogue: 0,0:42:26.20,0:42:32.02,Default,,0,0,0,,can't be changed well what you know me depending on what you're talking about physical mental
Dialogue: 0,0:42:32.02,0:42:39.63,Default,,0,0,0,,spiritual all right emotional of course everybody uh you know psychotherapy psychoanalysis group
Dialogue: 0,0:42:39.63,0:42:49.57,Default,,0,0,0,,therapy consciousness raising programs are all aimed at lifting us and making us more
Dialogue: 0,0:42:49.57,0:42:53.93,Default,,0,0,0,,aware and more loving and more helpful and more beneficial to others yes
Dialogue: 0,0:42:53.93,0:43:06.33,Default,,0,0,0,,mm-hmm okay so if we take a mental inventory of how we are in the world would that change the
Dialogue: 0,0:43:06.33,0:43:09.52,Default,,0,0,0,,world that does already change the world yes
Dialogue: 0,0:43:09.52,0:43:10.80,Default,,0,0,0,,because
Dialogue: 0,0:43:10.80,0:43:14.06,Default,,0,0,0,,because everybody's consciousness is interconnected you might say
Dialogue: 0,0:43:14.06,0:43:21.29,Default,,0,0,0,,in some minimal degree to everybody else's so everyone who takes responsibility
Dialogue: 0,0:43:21.29,0:43:27.06,Default,,0,0,0,,for the way they are in the world and their degree of lovingness and upliftingness
Dialogue: 0,0:43:27.06,0:43:31.22,Default,,0,0,0,,is already changing the world by just taking responsibility for it
Dialogue: 0,0:43:31.22,0:43:35.02,Default,,0,0,0,,to see that you're playing a part in it already changes
Dialogue: 0,0:43:35.02,0:43:41.38,Default,,0,0,0,,uh already changes that so when i have that knee-jerk reaction that i just want to smash
Dialogue: 0,0:43:41.38,0:43:43.94,Default,,0,0,0,,someone
Dialogue: 0,0:43:43.94,0:43:50.82,Default,,0,0,0,,all right so if i change that reaction that will change that's right who i am which changes the
Dialogue: 0,0:43:50.82,0:43:57.58,Default,,0,0,0,,world that's the way it works mm-hmm darn it the better we get the better we get because the better
Dialogue: 0,0:43:57.58,0:44:00.38,Default,,0,0,0,,we get the better we are and the better we are the better we get
Dialogue: 0,0:44:04.78,0:44:11.26,Default,,0,0,0,,yeah it's it's hard to do that though you know you have to i mean especially when you want to do you
Dialogue: 0,0:44:11.26,0:44:18.27,Default,,0,0,0,,I mean, you would like to be able to say, to be that person that sits back and says,
Dialogue: 0,0:44:18.91,0:44:22.21,Default,,0,0,0,,oh, I'm glad to see you feel that way.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:23.79,0:44:25.45,Default,,0,0,0,,You know, you want to go, hmm.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:25.87,0:44:28.55,Default,,0,0,0,,It's kind of like that joke someone gave me, you know.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:29.01,0:44:34.01,Default,,0,0,0,,I meditate, I burn candles, and something else, what is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:44:34.35,0:44:39.39,Default,,0,0,0,,I meditate, burn candles, and drink green tea, and I still want to smack someone.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:41.29,0:44:45.37,Default,,0,0,0,,That's funny, yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:46.65,0:44:48.59,Default,,0,0,0,,I know, I have that on my refrigerator.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:48.97,0:44:49.53,Default,,0,0,0,,That's funny.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:52.96,0:44:54.22,Default,,0,0,0,,So, you know.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:54.50,0:44:55.62,Default,,0,0,0,,We laugh at ourselves.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:55.82,0:44:59.08,Default,,0,0,0,,So laughing at ourselves is a sign of emotional maturity.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:00.35,0:45:05.33,Default,,0,0,0,,To detach from yourself, be able to laugh at yourself, laugh at your own foibles,
Dialogue: 0,0:45:05.33,0:45:10.23,Default,,0,0,0,,be self-forgiving for your limitations, accept the fact you're not perfect,
Dialogue: 0,0:45:11.03,0:45:12.61,Default,,0,0,0,,and that you're just...
Dialogue: 0,0:45:12.63,0:45:15.73,Default,,0,0,0,,that you're not just human, but that you're lovable and worthwhile,
Dialogue: 0,0:45:16.31,0:45:20.39,Default,,0,0,0,,and so your self-regard increases when you accept your limitations
Dialogue: 0,0:45:20.39,0:45:24.39,Default,,0,0,0,,as part of being inherent to the human condition itself.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:25.09,0:45:29.52,Default,,0,0,0,,So if you were to give us a...
Dialogue: 0,0:45:30.22,0:45:35.16,Default,,0,0,0,,condense all this into one thing on...
Dialogue: 0,0:45:35.93,0:45:41.15,Default,,0,0,0,,as to what we should do to improve ourselves, what would that be?
Dialogue: 0,0:45:41.15,0:45:43.07,Default,,0,0,0,,To be as loving as possible.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:43.71,0:45:45.31,Default,,0,0,0,,To be as loving as possible.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:45.97,0:45:49.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Loving and forgiving and caring as possible.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:49.71,0:45:51.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Even though we make mistakes.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:51.45,0:45:53.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, even though you make mistakes.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:54.03,0:45:56.07,Default,,0,0,0,,We have to forgive ourselves for that.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:57.07,0:45:57.87,Default,,0,0,0,,That's right.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:58.01,0:46:02.41,Default,,0,0,0,,So we try to be the best person we can in all circumstances,
Dialogue: 0,0:46:02.85,0:46:04.83,Default,,0,0,0,,and of course we will fall short,
Dialogue: 0,0:46:06.37,0:46:10.31,Default,,0,0,0,,but our motivation is, you know, correct.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:12.03,0:46:15.41,Default,,0,0,0,,You may forget the speedometer and get over the speed limit a few miles,
Dialogue: 0,0:46:15.53,0:46:15.89,Default,,0,0,0,,but then a little...
Dialogue: 0,0:46:16.57,0:46:19.57,Default,,0,0,0,,a little way down the road, you suddenly can pull yourself back and say,
Dialogue: 0,0:46:20.13,0:46:22.05,Default,,0,0,0,,hey, I'm picking up speed, I better slow down.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:22.35,0:46:28.80,Default,,0,0,0,,So self-awareness, then, is the guide that we turn to.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:29.40,0:46:31.64,Default,,0,0,0,,In the end, we turn to ourself anyway.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:31.88,0:46:32.78,Default,,0,0,0,,You turn to yourself.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:33.88,0:46:38.34,Default,,0,0,0,,It isn't just what others say, it's what others say affects us
Dialogue: 0,0:46:38.34,0:46:42.14,Default,,0,0,0,,that gives them the power to influence our lives.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:42.14,0:46:46.36,Default,,0,0,0,,If we don't care about what they think, it would have no effect.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:47.56,0:46:53.71,Default,,0,0,0,,So caring about others, then, is the best way to achieve happiness
Dialogue: 0,0:46:53.71,0:46:55.91,Default,,0,0,0,,for yourself and everyone around you.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:55.91,0:47:03.18,Default,,0,0,0,,That way your life becomes a gift to the world.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:03.18,0:47:06.52,Default,,0,0,0,,So you...
Dialogue: 0,0:47:06.52,0:47:09.72,Default,,0,0,0,,In an overall field, you can say to yourself,
Dialogue: 0,0:47:09.72,0:47:15.72,Default,,0,0,0,,how am I being of gift to the world, to my family, to my neighbors,
Dialogue: 0,0:47:15.72,0:47:17.72,Default,,0,0,0,,to the world in general?
Dialogue: 0,0:47:17.72,0:47:21.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Am I a detriment to the world or a gift to the world?
Dialogue: 0,0:47:21.67,0:47:24.85,Default,,0,0,0,,A detriment or a gift?
Dialogue: 0,0:47:24.95,0:47:32.95,Default,,0,0,0,,So it would be through prayer, actions, service, thoughts,
Dialogue: 0,0:47:32.95,0:47:37.95,Default,,0,0,0,,that you become this person who changes the world and changes yourself.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:37.95,0:47:39.95,Default,,0,0,0,,That's the way it works.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:39.95,0:47:46.27,Default,,0,0,0,,Because what we become subtly influences the world.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:47.82,0:47:49.82,Default,,0,0,0,,What we say we are can be refuted,
Dialogue: 0,0:47:49.82,0:47:54.91,Default,,0,0,0,,but what we actually are actually does change the world.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:54.91,0:47:55.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's see.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:55.91,0:47:59.91,Default,,0,0,0,,What we actually are actually changes the world.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:59.91,0:48:01.91,Default,,0,0,0,,It's good to know.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:01.91,0:48:08.65,Default,,0,0,0,,So it's important to be kindly to the animals in the woods.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:08.65,0:48:14.71,Default,,0,0,0,,It's important to be kindly to the field, to the tree, and to the bushes.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:14.71,0:48:20.13,Default,,0,0,0,,So our kindness radiates out into the world.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:20.13,0:48:22.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Our kindness.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:22.13,0:48:27.77,Default,,0,0,0,,The best thing we can do for the woods is to love it and appreciate it.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:27.77,0:48:33.38,Default,,0,0,0,,And it's very exciting.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:33.38,0:48:36.38,Default,,0,0,0,,And then you find that there's a hidden love in that existence.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:36.38,0:48:39.58,Default,,0,0,0,,As you're busy walking through the woods all by yourself,
Dialogue: 0,0:48:39.58,0:48:43.96,Default,,0,0,0,,loving the beauty and the leaves falling in the fall,
Dialogue: 0,0:48:43.96,0:48:45.96,Default,,0,0,0,,and you hear the rustling and the incredible beauty,
Dialogue: 0,0:48:45.96,0:48:49.96,Default,,0,0,0,,all of a sudden a sort of a thrill shoots through you.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:49.96,0:48:56.41,Default,,0,0,0,,You realize that your lovingness of nature is partly why it is what it is.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:56.41,0:48:59.41,Default,,0,0,0,,It's because you are part of nature.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:59.41,0:49:01.41,Default,,0,0,0,,So it's not you and nature.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:01.41,0:49:03.41,Default,,0,0,0,,It's you as nature.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:03.41,0:49:07.70,Default,,0,0,0,,And you realize that you are part of nature.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:07.70,0:49:13.70,Default,,0,0,0,,And that your love is benefiting all the trees and bushes and everything around you.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:13.70,0:49:19.43,Default,,0,0,0,,So your love actually does nourish the world.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:19.43,0:49:21.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Your love nourishes the world.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:21.43,0:49:25.69,Default,,0,0,0,,Therefore, instead of minimizing that, you know,
Dialogue: 0,0:49:25.69,0:49:32.07,Default,,0,0,0,,appreciate the fact that who you are is influencing the world for the better or for worse.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:32.07,0:49:36.65,Default,,0,0,0,,And in the end, we're answerable for that.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:36.65,0:49:44.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Are the trees glad to see me today or not?
Dialogue: 0,0:49:44.01,0:49:48.10,Default,,0,0,0,,I want the trees to be glad to see me.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:48.10,0:49:51.10,Default,,0,0,0,,There's an old duck walking through the woods there.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:51.10,0:49:53.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's see.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:53.10,0:49:55.10,Default,,0,0,0,,And the trees say, oh, goody.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:55.10,0:49:58.10,Default,,0,0,0,,There you go.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:58.10,0:50:00.23,Default,,0,0,0,,So it's not just ego.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:00.23,0:50:02.23,Default,,0,0,0,,It's a fact of nature.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:02.23,0:50:03.23,Default,,0,0,0,,All right.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:03.23,0:50:05.55,Default,,0,0,0,,So it's a fact of nature.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:05.55,0:50:06.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Nature.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:06.55,0:50:19.07,Default,,0,0,0,,The totality is conscious and aware of what is in its presence for the better or for worse.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:19.07,0:50:23.52,Default,,0,0,0,,So that nature shudders at the presence of the evil doer.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:23.52,0:50:24.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Resist.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:24.52,0:50:31.55,Default,,0,0,0,,There you go.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:31.55,0:50:34.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Nature shudders at the presence of certain people.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:34.55,0:50:36.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Wow.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:36.35,0:50:43.31,Default,,0,0,0,,Wouldn't that be awful to be a person that even nature is scared of you?
Dialogue: 0,0:50:43.31,0:50:44.31,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, dear.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:44.31,0:50:45.31,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, dear.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:45.31,0:50:52.27,Default,,0,0,0,,No, I spent a lot of time walking through woods by myself.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:52.27,0:50:58.75,Default,,0,0,0,,And I was always aware of the beauty and the fact that nature was conscious of my presence somehow.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:58.75,0:51:07.68,Default,,0,0,0,,And I always sent love to the trees and the bushes and radiated my appreciation.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:07.68,0:51:12.03,Default,,0,0,0,,And of course, in the end, all of that is divinity.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:12.03,0:51:16.64,Default,,0,0,0,,So what you're doing is what you're catching onto is the divinity of the existence.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:16.64,0:51:20.64,Default,,0,0,0,,The divinity of the existence of life itself.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:20.64,0:51:27.63,Default,,0,0,0,,And the feedback then tends to increase that value.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:27.63,0:51:33.02,Default,,0,0,0,,So you're alive, but you're not only alive, but you're glad that you're alive.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:33.02,0:51:39.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Lots of people drag themselves through life and they don't seem to be very glad that they're alive.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:42.82,0:51:48.02,Default,,0,0,0,,They're glad that they're alive.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:48.02,0:51:50.02,Default,,0,0,0,,So when you say be as loving and kind.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:50.02,0:51:58.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Be as loving and kind to everything and respect its existence.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:58.11,0:51:59.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, that's right.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:59.11,0:52:02.11,Default,,0,0,0,,You're actually saying that is what you want to become.
Dialogue: 0,0:52:02.11,0:52:06.52,Default,,0,0,0,,And that is actually changing the world.
Dialogue: 0,0:52:06.52,0:52:10.52,Default,,0,0,0,,I was thinking of the story of that little woman who was black, I think.
Dialogue: 0,0:52:10.52,0:52:12.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Very small, little 70-year-old lady.
Dialogue: 0,0:52:12.52,0:52:13.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Right.
Dialogue: 0,0:52:13.62,0:52:15.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Who refused to give up her seat.
Dialogue: 0,0:52:15.62,0:52:16.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:52:16.62,0:52:17.62,Default,,0,0,0,,On the bus.
Dialogue: 0,0:52:17.62,0:52:21.13,Default,,0,0,0,,And, you know, anyway.
Dialogue: 0,0:52:21.13,0:52:24.13,Default,,0,0,0,,I always think of the effect that she had.
Dialogue: 0,0:52:24.13,0:52:25.13,Default,,0,0,0,,That one action.
Dialogue: 0,0:52:25.13,0:52:27.13,Default,,0,0,0,,That she would not go to the back of the bus.
Dialogue: 0,0:52:27.13,0:52:29.13,Default,,0,0,0,,That one action.
Dialogue: 0,0:52:29.13,0:52:33.13,Default,,0,0,0,,And that little lady who weighed, I forget how many pounds she weighed.
Dialogue: 0,0:52:33.13,0:52:34.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:52:34.13,0:52:38.22,Default,,0,0,0,,A very small little lady who didn't weigh hardly anything.
Dialogue: 0,0:52:38.22,0:52:41.22,Default,,0,0,0,,You know, profoundly changed society and the world.
Dialogue: 0,0:52:41.22,0:52:43.22,Default,,0,0,0,,And how they look at things, yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:52:43.22,0:52:46.47,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:52:46.47,0:52:50.47,Default,,0,0,0,,So if we love ourself, we realize that we are of importance.
Dialogue: 0,0:52:50.47,0:52:53.82,Default,,0,0,0,,So there's sort of a soothing.
Dialogue: 0,0:52:53.82,0:52:54.82,Default,,0,0,0,,A pseudo-humbleness.
Dialogue: 0,0:52:54.82,0:52:55.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, I'm nobody.
Dialogue: 0,0:52:55.82,0:53:02.16,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't really amount to anything.
Dialogue: 0,0:53:02.16,0:53:08.16,Default,,0,0,0,,The truth of it is that who you are and how you are that is profoundly affecting.
Dialogue: 0,0:53:08.16,0:53:11.16,Default,,0,0,0,,And it's not grandiosity or egotism.
Dialogue: 0,0:53:11.16,0:53:18.48,Default,,0,0,0,,In fact, it's humility that allows you to say, yes, who I am and how I am that does
Dialogue: 0,0:53:18.48,0:53:22.48,Default,,0,0,0,,have an effect on the world and take responsibility for it.
Dialogue: 0,0:53:22.48,0:53:28.26,Default,,0,0,0,,So, thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:53:28.26,0:53:29.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:53:29.42,0:53:30.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:53:30.42,0:53:31.93,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:53:31.93,0:53:41.28,Default,,0,0,0,,And so, we'll be doing these little what we call fireside chats this year.
Dialogue: 0,0:53:41.28,0:53:42.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh.
Dialogue: 0,0:53:42.28,0:53:45.28,Default,,0,0,0,,And we'll have hopefully another two.
Dialogue: 0,0:53:45.28,0:53:46.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh.
Dialogue: 0,0:53:46.28,0:53:47.28,Default,,0,0,0,,This year.
Dialogue: 0,0:53:47.28,0:53:54.41,Default,,0,0,0,,So we'll be happy that we're condensing our material down to where I think that it'll
Dialogue: 0,0:53:54.41,0:53:58.41,Default,,0,0,0,,be good for our followers to be able to look at it.
Dialogue: 0,0:53:58.41,0:54:01.41,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, well that'll be fun.
Dialogue: 0,0:54:01.41,0:54:02.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:54:02.76,0:54:03.76,Default,,0,0,0,,That'll be fun.
Dialogue: 0,0:54:03.76,0:54:04.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you very much.
